title: [Western Waterway, Harbor]
description: Large chunks of the same limestone as the cliffs to the north tumble over each other to the southeast, thrusting a protective arm around the harbor.  Waves break against the weathered ivory of the jetty's surface, and a lone lantern flickers in the darkness of night, casting its pallid light over the rolling surf.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, southwest, west, northwest
